Now you're holding onto Yi

613
00:30:26,279 --> 00:30:26,700
like he's your daddy.

614
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:28,480
It's food poisoning, OK?!

615
00:30:32,319 --> 00:30:32,880
You OK?

616
00:30:33,059 --> 00:30:33,599
Thanks.

617
00:30:34,059 --> 00:30:34,480
I'm good.

618
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,140
Wash your mouth.

619
00:30:35,599 --> 00:30:36,680
Got a free spot here!

620
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,000
I'm riding with them.

621
00:30:38,099 --> 00:30:38,920
Get some sleep, kid.

622
00:30:39,119 --> 00:30:39,759
He thinks

623
00:30:39,759 --> 00:30:40,799
I'm gonna puke in the car?

624
00:30:41,519 --> 00:30:42,160
Get in.

625
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:52,359
Pretty tight here, don't you think?

626
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:56,480
The wind wrecked my eyes.

627
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,559
The glare in the front

628
00:30:58,740 --> 00:31:00,200
will blind me.

629
00:31:00,799 --> 00:31:01,599
If you need room,

630
00:31:01,599 --> 00:31:02,460
be my guest.

631
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:07,319
You've had a long weekend

632
00:31:07,319 --> 00:31:08,460
hosting us.

633
00:31:09,119 --> 00:31:10,319
Shotgun's got the visor.

634
00:31:10,619 --> 00:31:11,420
Plenty of room.

635
00:31:11,660 --> 00:31:12,400
It's perfect

636
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:13,539
for a nap.

637
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:16,640
Enough!

638
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:18,000
Let me out.

639
00:31:18,819 --> 00:31:19,559
I'll take shotgun.

640
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:20,920
You two can hold hands back here.

641
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:23,640
Move!

642
00:31:50,660 --> 00:31:51,160
Let's roll.

643
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:06,039
Mr. Cen,

644
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:07,859
your hotel is

645
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,019
in the opposite direction, right?

646
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:12,579
Drop her off first.

647
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:13,880
Then I'll head back.

648
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:32,000
Thanks.

649
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:35,240
Take this.

650
00:33:12,700 --> 00:33:13,799
My back is killing me.

651
00:33:14,980 --> 00:33:15,859
Get some sleep.

652
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:16,779
You too.

653
00:33:17,079 --> 00:33:17,740
See you.

654
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,799
Goodbye.

655
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:19,799
Also...

656
00:33:28,319 --> 00:33:28,980
Let's go.

657
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:30,400
Sure.

658
00:35:02,539 --> 00:35:04,099
[You act like]

659
00:35:05,300 --> 00:35:06,519
[a shield,]

660
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,639
[but who]

661
00:35:11,019 --> 00:35:12,159
[protects you?]

662
00:35:19,079 --> 00:35:20,719
[Sometimes I don't know]

663
00:35:21,260 --> 00:35:22,440
[if you're being selfless,]

664
00:35:22,980 --> 00:35:23,980
[or just selfish.]

665
00:35:25,460 --> 00:35:26,820
[You love me,]

666
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,840
[but you're so terrible at showing it.]

667
00:35:59,159 --> 00:36:00,199
Are you alright?

668
00:36:01,039 --> 00:36:02,219
You've been quiet.

669
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,519
Soup's ready, eat some.

670
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:09,559
I'm fine.

671
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:18,679
Something bothering you?

672
00:36:21,519 --> 00:36:22,559
It's gonna storm.

673
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:23,739
I'll get the clothes inside.

674
00:36:32,780 --> 00:36:33,860
She seems off...

675
00:36:35,599 --> 00:36:36,599
[Attention everyone:]

676
00:36:36,880 --> 00:36:38,260
[a Category Four typhoon]

677
00:36:38,260 --> 00:36:38,960
[is expected to]

678
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:40,460
[hit the city tonight.]

679
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:42,260
[We anticipate]

680
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:43,260
[heavy storm surges.]

681
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:44,920
[Please avoid all travel]

682
00:36:45,079 --> 00:36:45,920
[and stay indoors.]

683
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,239
[I bought this for you.]

684
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,599
[Oh, wow! Thank you!]

685
00:37:38,159 --> 00:37:38,840
[Show us!]

686
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,000
[Back off,]

687
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:41,440
[boys!]

688
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:42,639
[Girls only.]

689
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:44,300
[Sweetie,]

690
00:37:44,460 --> 00:37:45,119
[Happy New Year!]

691
00:37:45,199 --> 00:37:45,960
[Happy New Year!]

692
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:12,119
[To me, he was invincible.]

693
00:38:13,019 --> 00:38:14,119
[I believed he could]

694
00:38:14,119 --> 00:38:15,059
[outrun any storm.]

695
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:25,840
[Don't worry about]

696
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:26,860
[the tuition.]

697
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:28,840
[I've got you.]

698
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:41,400
[Here's your school money.]

699
00:38:44,599 --> 00:38:46,219
[It's clean. I swear.]

700
00:39:22,380 --> 00:39:23,139
[Get into]

701
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:24,199
[a good college.]

702
00:39:24,599 --> 00:39:25,599
[I'll buy you a gold one.]

703
00:39:26,199 --> 00:39:27,059
[At least this thick.]

704
00:39:30,260 --> 00:39:31,119
[But Chen Yi...]

705
00:39:32,079 --> 00:39:33,440
[do you have any idea]

706
00:39:34,559 --> 00:39:35,579
[how much it burns]

707
00:39:35,579 --> 00:39:37,360
[to live in a future...]

708
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:39,039
[built on your scars?]

709
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:02,619
[Chen Yi...]

710
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:06,400
[I came back thinking]

711
00:41:08,679 --> 00:41:09,480
[I could rescue you.]

712
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:10,880
[But I was being arrogant.]

713
00:41:13,860 --> 00:41:14,739
[All I'm doing is]

714
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:19,119
[causing you]

715
00:41:21,159 --> 00:41:22,119
[more pain.]

716
00:41:27,739 --> 00:41:29,260
[I'd go through it all again. Gladly.]

717
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:34,800
[If I walk out of your life...]

718
00:41:35,980 --> 00:41:36,440
[will you finally]

719
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:38,099
[stop bleeding for me?]
